name: The Magical Item #9: Fara: The Magic Sauce
description: Dino finally reaches Fara, the 9th Magical Location where he meets the four wild Rabtoz. With the help of the Jaru Fairy, Dino connects himself to Cooko, a motherboard that allows him to create a Magic Sauce derived from his power and that can turn any wild creature into a domestic one. The four Rabtoz devour the Magic Sauce and join Dino's crew in their journey. Unlocking this portal will increase your Attraction Attribute by 670 MPs.
